There's another thing.

94
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,520
If you promise me this,

95
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,640
I'll marry you.

96
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,600
- I'll promise anything.
- I can tell you

97
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,520
my revenge plan,

98
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:45,680
