I don't want to drag you down.

100
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:01,160
Yunxi.

101
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:04,240
You've had a really hard time.

102
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,000
As your husband,

103
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:08,000
