104
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:12,880
Yanyu.

105
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,400
You know me well.

106
00:07:16,640 --> 00:07:18,040
I'll never back out,

107
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,840
