108
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,320
breaking up with Xiao Chuyi,

109
00:07:24,320 --> 00:07:25,200
or

110
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:26,760
fulfilling my promise to you.

111
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:29,680
The granary

112
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,440
