of the political in-fighting,

113
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,840
and it's dangerous.

114
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,560
Standing out at this point

115
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:36,000
is like dancing on a knife edge.

116
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,760
If you fall, you'll be cut into pieces.

117
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:40,920
I understand.

118
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:43,560
I've waited for seven years.

119
00:07:43,840 --> 00:07:45,560
Now that we've made some progress,

120
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:46,680
I can't give up at this point.

121
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:48,560
However,

122
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:51,120
